onments, through\nthe directional or speed persistence or the speed-direction correlation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 May 2022 10:24:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2022 18:57:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-23"}
