ge-region method are applied to an LES of a wind farm operating\nin a conventionally neutral boundary layer, for which we measure a reflectivity\nof only 0.75%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 May 2022 14:39:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Sep 2022 09:50:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-02"}
